description.en: Picarto is the world’s leading live streaming platform for creative minds. Come join us and watch artists from all over the world during their creative process!
description.ga_IE: Is é Picarto ardán sruthú beo an domhain le haghaidh aigne cruthaitheacha.Tar isteach linn agus féachaint ar ealaíontóirí ó gach cearn den domhan le linn a bpróiseas cruthaitheach!
